articles.title: Five Americans detained in Iran expected to be freed Monday, Iranian foreign ministry says - CNN

articles.title: Soyuz docks at International Space Station with two Russians, one American - Fox News
articles.description: Russia's Soyuz MS-24 blasted off from Kazakhstan Friday with two Russian cosmonauts and one American astronaut on board and landed at the International Space Station three hours later.
articles.content:
A Russian spacecraft carrying two Russians and an American docked at the International Space Station on Friday after blasting off from Kazakhstan.
